summary:
Just a enb preset.
<br /><br />To install paste the folder into your Skyrim main folder and click yes to override.
<br /><br />
descriptionHtml:
You dont have to download nmb. It is included already. Just copy and paste into your main skyrim folder.
In your skyrim.prefs change to:
bTreesReceiveShadows=1bDrawLandShadows=1bShadowsOnGrass=1
bFloatPointRenderTarget=1
In your enblocal change to:
ReservedMemorySizeMb=x (1GB change to 128, 2-256, 3-512, 4-1024)
VideoMemorySizeMb=x according to your video card memory<br />
<br />recomended mods:
<br />Skyrim 2k textures
<br />W.E.A.T.E.R.
<br />Real Clouds
<br />
